  "body": "# Problem\r\nFrequent comments on screen shots not being allowed. Current copy `Hide Status previews when app switching` is long, making it difficult to understand at glance. Also the copy doesn't capture the primary use case of Allow/Disallow screenshots.\r\n\r\nHide Status previews can be seen as a side effect of disallowing screenshots on Android. On iOS screenshots will still be allowed\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\nDue to different OS behavior, show more representative copy by platform\r\nAndroid copy change:\r\n- Current `Hide Status previews when app switching`\r\n- Expected: `Block screenshots`\r\n\r\niOS copy change:\r\n- Current `Hide Status previews when app switching`\r\n- Expected: `Hide previews`",
